{"word":"Linen","slug":"linen","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Linen</b> Exported from:<br/> - Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=28'>1Ki 10:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=7'>Eze 27:7</a> <br/> - Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=16'>Eze 27:16</a> <br/> Curtains of the tabernacle made of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=1'>Exo 26:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=27&verse=9'>Exo 27:9</a><br/> Vestments of priests made of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=8'>Exo 28:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=15'>Exo 28:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=42'>Exo 28:42</a><br/> Livery of royal households made of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=42'>Gen 41:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=8&verse=15'>Est 8:15</a><br/> Garments made of:<br/> - For men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=42'>Gen 41:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=9&verse=2'>Eze 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=16&verse=19'>Luk 16:19</a> <br/> - For women<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=23'>Isa 3:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=13'>Eze 16:13</a> <br/> Bedding made of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=7&verse=16'>Pro 7:16</a><br/> Mosaic law forbade its being mingled with wool<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=19'>Lev 19:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=11'>Deu 22:11</a><br/> The body of Jesus wrapped in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=46'>Mar 15:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=5'>Joh 20:5</a><br/> Figurative, pure and white, of righteousness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=15&verse=6'>Rev 15:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=19&verse=8'>Rev 19:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=19&verse=14'>Rev 19:14</a>"}]}